{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2018}} {{Infobox person |image = | name = John Aldred | birth_date = 1921 | birth_place = [[Doncaster]], England | death_date = | death_place = | occupation = [[audio engineering|Sound engineer]] | yearsactive = 1942-1973 }}
'''John B Aldred''' (born 1921) is an English [[audio engineering|sound engineer]]. He was nominated for two [[Academy Awards]] in the category [[Academy Award for Best Sound Mixing|Sound Recording]]. He worked on 57 different films and TV shows from 1942 to 1973.
