{{Infobox person | image =Conductores 2015.png | imagesize = | caption = | birth_name = Micaela Belén Vázquez | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1986|11|24}} | birth_place = [[Buenos Aires]], [[Buenos Aires Province|Federal District]], [[Argentina]] | spouse = {{Marriage|Federico Larroca|2017}} | partner = [[Fernando Gago]] (2007-2010) | years active = 2001—present | goldenglobeawards = | awards = }}
'''Micaela Belén Vázquez''' (born November 24, 1986) is an [[Argentina|Argentine]] [[actress]]. She is the best known for her role of [[List of Rebelde Way characters|Pilar Dunoff]] in the series ''[[Rebelde Way]]'', and also for series ''[[Chiquititas]]'' and ''[[Floricienta]]'' — all created and produced by [[Cris Morena]]. From 2007 to 2010, Vázquez dated [[Real Madrid CF]] player [[Fernando Gago]].<ref name="WAG">''The Spoiler'': [http://www.thespoiler.co.uk/index.php/2009/07/15/wag-no-374-micaela-vazquez WAG No. 374: Micaela Vázquez] (15 July 2009)</ref><ref name="CD">''Comentario Deportivo'': [http://comentariodeportivo.com/noticias-deportivas/fernando-gago-se-anota-un-tanto-con-micaela-vazquez.html Fernando Gago se anota un tanto con Micaela Vázquez] {{webarchive|url=https://archive.is/20130119134042/http://comentariodeportivo.com/noticias-deportivas/fernando-gago-se-anota-un-tanto-con-micaela-vazquez.html |date=2013-01-19 }} (18 July 2009)</ref><ref name="GHM">''[[Don Balón]]'': [http://www.donbalon.com/web/noticia/i-148/gago-higuain-y-micaela Gago, Higuaín y Micaela] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091027044831/http://www.donbalon.com/web/noticia/i-148/gago-higuain-y-micaela |date=2009-10-27 }} (7 October 2009)</ref>
==Career== Vázquez was only ten when she landed the role of Miki in television hit series for children and teenagers, ''[[Chiquititas]]'', created by [[Cris Morena]]. Vázquez reprised her role on 2001 mini–series ''[[Chiquititas]]''. However, her most famous role is [[List of Rebelde Way characters#Pilar Dunoff|Pilar Dunoff]] in another Cris Morena's production, ''[[Rebelde Way]]'', co–starring [[Benjamin Rojas]], [[Luisana Lopilato]], [[Felipe Colombo]] and [[Camila Bordonaba]]. Vázques portrayed Pilar from 2002 to 2003, from the beginning until the very end. She was singing the back vocals at the two tours of ''Rebelde Way'' musical group, [[pop rock]] sensation [[Erreway]], [[Erreway en Grand Rex]] and [[Nuestro Tiempo]]. Vázquez also appeared in Erreway's videos "[[Sweet Baby (Erreway song)|Sweet Baby]]", "[[Resistiré (song)|Resistiré]]", "[[Tiempo (song)|Tiempo]]" and "[[Para Cosas Buenas]]".
In 2004, Vázquez appeared as Renata in television series ''[[Floricienta]]'', one more hit of [[Cris Morena]], co–starring [[Benjamin Rojas]], [[Florencia Bertotti]], [[Juan Gil Navarro]] and [[Isabel Macedo]]. In 2006, she appeared in film ''[[Crónica de una fuga]]''. Vázquez also had [[guest appearance]]s in hit television series such as ''[[Casados con Hijos (Argentina)|Casados con Hijos]]'' (2005), ''[[Sos mi vida]]'' (2006), ''[[Chiquititas|Chiqutitias 2006]]'' (2006) and ''[[Son de Fierro]]'' (2007).
==Personal life== Vázquez stated that her favorite sports are [[Team handball|handball]] and [[Association football|football]];<ref name="Micaela Vázquez">''Series Adictos'': [http://www.seriesadictos.com/rebelde-way/micaela-vazquez.php Micaela Vázquez]</ref> and supports football club [[Boca Juniors]].<ref name="Micaela Vázquez"/> From 2007 to 2010, she dated [[Real Madrid CF]] player [[Fernando Gago]],<ref name="WAG"/><ref name="CD"/><ref name="GHM"/> who left his girlfriend [[Silvina Luna]] for her.<ref name="Luna">''26 noticias'': [http://www.26noticias.com.ar/fernando-gago-dejo-a-silvina-luna-por-una-joven-actriz-14531.html Fernando Gago dejó a Silvina Luna por una joven actriz] (18 November 2007)</ref><ref name="DERF">''DERF'': [http://www.derf.com.ar/despachos.asp?cod_des=268609&ID_Seccion=17 Don Fernando y su botineras] (4 June 2009)</ref><ref name="Terra">''[[Terra Networks|Terra]]'': [http://www.terra.com.ar/canales/famosos/207/207313.html Micaela Vázquez, la chica que se disputan Gago e Higuaín]</ref><ref name="Perfil">''[[Perfil]]'': [http://www.diarioperfil.com.ar/edimp/0403/articulo.php?art=17078&ed=0403 La chica detrás de la pelea Gago–Higuaín] (26 September 2009)</ref> In 2009, it was reported Vázquez was involved with other Real Madrid Argentine player, [[Gonzalo Higuaín]],<ref name="Terra"/><ref name="Perfil"/> and Gago with Argentine tennis player [[Gisela Dulko]],<ref name="DERF"/> but the couple did not comment the rumours. In June 2010, Gago and Dulko came out as a couple.<ref name="DulkoyGago1">Terra.com: [http://www.terra.com.pe/deportes/noticias/dep813555/gisela-dulko-fernando-gago-demuestran-su-amor-twitter.html Gisela Dulko y Fernando Gago demuestran su amor en Twitter] (1 June 2010)</ref><ref name="DulkoyGago2">WTA Women Tennis.com: [http://wtawomenstennis.com/2010/11/photos-gisela-dulko-in-gente-magazine-with-boyfriend-fernando-gago/ Gisela Dulko in Gente Magazine with boyfriend, Fernando Gago] (25 November 2010)</ref>
